The paper discusses active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes a dynamic ensemble active learning algorithm based on a non-stationary multi-armed bandit with expert advice. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms)
